{"tid":2357903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年急救員認為死因研訊只還原了五成真相 對裁決「零期望」","createTime":"2021-01-07T18:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T05:10:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bb17dbdce5dba1041bcb5997cf2eb22fbdf27b","tid":2357903,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"早前先後主動聯絡死因庭提供資料及出庭作供的將軍澳街坊，及有份在現場治理梓樂的義務急救員，昨日均特意到庭旁聽裁判官引導陪審團。其中作供後獲裁判官盛讚可考慮做醫生的少年急救員（FA），認為是次研訊只還原了五成真相，對裁決「零期望」。<br />\n<br />\n17歲的曾朗軒昨披上黑色西裝外套旁聽，「想formal（正式）少少」，表示早上7時半已到達法院排隊輪候。他沒預測裁決結果，亦稱很難說會否受研訊結果影響情緒，自言抱觀望心態，對裁決「零期望」。他稱在庭上看到當晚的新聞片段時，不禁感到震撼，「真係每一刻都打緊仗」。朗軒認為，今次死因研訊只還原了五成真相，餘下四成是不知死者周梓樂墮樓前「消失的八秒」發生何事，最後一成是質疑警方有否盡力調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/NVO653PVP5BITHGWNUQQ2SRXJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FNVO653PVP5BITHGWNUQQ2SRXJU%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zz2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=a1422279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FNVO653PVP5BITHGWNUQQ2SRXJU%2F&h=9c82d9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/NVO653PVP5BITHGWNUQQ2SRXJU/</a>"},{"pid":"1aeeca36e4ac8230b09312307e6457c06873de77","tid":2357903,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916af672eef831bb64e87dd73ce048149959151a","tid":2357903,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32486108c070e6bf6aa367e3b22ba3f1d66ea5c","tid":2